Contrary to popular belief, the use of gadgets and technology was actually increasing the social interaction among seniors. 
Many felt a great sense of empowerment. 
They seemed to have regained a long lost sense of independence, while still being able to maintain a connection with their family and friends. 
YouTube gave them exposure to current affairs and world events and the ability to watch old movies from their youth. 
It kindled endless hours of gossip and discussions every day in the club house. 


A few months passed, and the news about Shanthi Vilas spread far and wide. 
Reporters hungry for a news story made a beeline to the senior citizens' colony. 
They were eager to speak to the mastermind of this remarkable transformation, WhatsApp Vasan.